					<br />
					<hr size="2" width="100%" />
					Title: <b>Re: bitcoin-qt email notification when payment sent or received possible?</b><br />
					Post by: <b>BitBlitz</b> on <b>October 26, 2012, 03:35:20 PM</b>
					<hr />
					<div style="margin: 0 5ex;">I do this with my blockchain.info account.&nbsp; Just add your local wallet address to the blockchain account as &quot;Watch Only&quot; and enable email or SMS notification.</div>
